  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Type 2 diabetes patients have a high risk of developing NAFLD. This was confirmed during&#xD;
      previous research, a high prevalence of NAFLD among type 2 diabetes mellitus patients was&#xD;
      found. The investigators want to determine the characteristics of this population.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
